    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"130609\">@Antoine Chambert-Loir</span>, I'm confused by that comment, as both <span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"197836\">Jireh Loreaux</span> and <span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"260507\">Heather Macbeth</span>'s versions above use <code>T : V â†’â‚—[ğ•œ] W</code> already.</p>",
